{"tid":1635834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家一定要注意馬路上面旅遊巴","createTime":"2019-10-07T15:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T05:58:45.000Z","uid":30635,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f3822de78a404ec024b7be815b0785b89d2ba01a","tid":1635834,"uid":30635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:23:31.000Z","msg":"岩岩好多屯門手足係一條直路到 <br />\n明明無任何大廈出入口 以為好完全既情況下<br />\n突然唔知係邊出現左一堆速龍<br />\n一落車就係咁射胡椒彈 <br />\n後面聽人講係旅遊巴跑落黎<br />\n痴撚線 真係好撚恐怖<br />\n<br />\n大家而家唔止大廈出入口<br />\n連馬路上面既車都要定要留意<br />\n我見岩岩有圖係密斗搵速龍<br />\n佢地已經無晒底線咁突襲我地<br />\n求下大家要小心 岩岩屯門已經無左十幾廿個手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d08097cd209a93d5a1247ca87266798cc05dce9","tid":1635834,"uid":30635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:24:51.000Z","msg":"推呀屌"},{"pid":"d3eb50c38fb319ba88cdb8e3bf18a56fde0a29e4","tid":1635834,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:25:49.000Z","msg":"真手足"},{"pid":"649ea2761f8680a9748eba21595d9324fbdd80fe","tid":1635834,"uid":31151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:27:03.000Z","msg":"私家車 7人家 貨車 貨櫃車 旅遊巴 全部都要小心啦唔理佢咩顏色<br />\n總知睇唔到有咩人坐既全部要小心"},{"pid":"258193f3fcc5ef475e01f8beb78a650e9ba10894","tid":1635834,"uid":30635,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:28:29.000Z","msg":"屌那星 班狗而家好撚陰濕<br />\n大家要睇住馬路既所有車"},{"pid":"616eb620acbc01397a8753955cc72385a4cb74bb","tid":1635834,"uid":156587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:29:21.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbeb372947835e772676be8d519e9c20d816fed0","tid":1635834,"uid":302449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:30:01.